Package ElectronicAssetTradingPlatform.Users

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ITAdmin
    ITAdmin class which extends the user class.
    OrganisationalUnitLeader
    Class for the organisational unit leaders Organisanational unit leaders are part of the organisational unit, however they have additional capabilities over ordinary members.
    OrganisationalUnitMembers
    OrganisationalUnitMembers class which extends the user class.
    SystemsAdmin
    Class for Systems Admin users allowing for all users with this access level to be able to create new Organisational Units, be able to edit their respective Assets and Credits along with having the ability to create new asset types and new uses accounts with up to the same level of access privileges.
    User
    Class for the users of the application
    UsersFactory
    Class to create new users of a specific type
